{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-js","path":"/uses/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"What tech do you use?","date":"2016-08-26T00:00:00.000Z","date_pretty":"August 26th, 2016","date_from_now":"4 years ago","last_modified_at":"2020-01-13T14:56:34.000Z","last_modified_at_from_now":"6 months ago","path":"/uses/","excerpt":"A list detailing my developer setup, gear, software, and preferred configurations.","toc":null,"image":null},"id":"a3203a2c-dc57-5974-8b86-2c70ba7958c6","html":"<p>Read on friend to learn about the hardware and software I use for play and to build Made Mistakes. None of it is terribly exciting or unexpected, but hey — maybe the curious of you will find it interesting.</p>\n<h2 id=\"hardware\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hardware\" aria-label=\"hardware permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Hardware</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>iMac 21.5-inch</strong>, Late 2013 model with 16GB memory, and stock Apple Magic Mouse and keyboard.</li>\n<li><strong>Lenovo ThinkStation E30</strong>, 3.30 GHz Intel Xeon with 16 GB memory.</li>\n<li><strong>iPad 12.9″ Pro</strong> with the Space Gray finish and Apple Pencil (first generation).</li>\n<li><strong>iPhone 7 Plus</strong> with Jet Black finish.</li>\n<li><strong>Apple Watch Series 5</strong> with Space Gray aluminum case.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://amzn.to/2R4A1YC\"><strong>Canon Rebel XTi DSLR Camera</strong></a> with EF-S 18-55mm and 50mm lenses.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"design-and-development\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#design-and-development\" aria-label=\"design and development permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Design and development</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Operating systems: <strong>macOS Mojave</strong> and <strong>Windows 7</strong></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/\"><strong>Visual Studio Code</strong></a> with the following notable extensions:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=ms-vscode.Theme-MaterialKit\"><strong>Material Theme Kit</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=eamodio.gitlens\"><strong>GitLens</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=travisthetechie.write-good-linter\"><strong>Write Good Linter</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=jsynowiec.vscode-insertdatestring\"><strong>Insert Date String</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=Tyriar.lorem-ipsum\"><strong>Lorem ipsum</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=bierner.markdown-preview-github-styles\"><strong>Markdown Preview GitHub Styling</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=AlanWalk.markdown-toc\"><strong>Markdown TOC</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=Shan.code-settings-sync\"><strong>Settings Sync</strong></a></li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.sourcetreeapp.com/\"><strong>Sourcetree</strong></a> for Git heavy lifting when VS Code doesn’t cut it.</li>\n<li><strong>Adobe Creative Suite</strong> - Photoshop, Illustrator, and occasionally AfterEffects.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://jekyllrb.com/\"><strong>Jekyll</strong></a> - Ruby based static site generator.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/\"><strong>Gatsby</strong></a> - React based framework for building websites and apps.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>I’ve been on a <a href=\"/articles/going-static/\">static site generator</a> kick the last couple of years and use <s><a href=\"https://jekyllrb.com/\"><strong>Jekyll</strong></a></s> <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/\"><strong>Gatsby</strong></a> to build this page and everything else found on the site. The basic idea is I write a bunch of text in Markdown and it spits out a set of files that are deployed to a webserver.</p>\n<p>If you’re interested in the specifics of how the site is built I’ve made its <a href=\"https://github.com/mmistakes/made-mistakes-gatsby\">source available on GitHub</a> for anyone to fork and download. And because I’m such a cool dude I’ve also open sourced a couple of <a href=\"/work/jekyll-themes/\">Jekyll themes</a> for you to use and abuse — you’re welcome!</p>\n<h2 id=\"other-software\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#other-software\" aria-label=\"other software permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Other software</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://bitwarden.com/\"><strong>BitWarden</strong></a> - password manager.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://secure.backblaze.com/r/014jkj\"><strong>Backblaze</strong></a> - cloud backups.</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"three-column\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; background-color: var(--input-background-color); max-width: 800px;\">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 177.8181818181818%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image lazyload\" alt=\"my iPhone home screen apps\" title=\"my iPhone home screen apps\" data-src=\"/static/a1514d8f47c7bf38b8fd13c0cada115b/b1bff/iphone-home-screen-1.jpg\" data-srcset=\"/static/a1514d8f47c7bf38b8fd13c0cada115b/16841/iphone-home-screen-1.jpg 275w,\n/static/a1514d8f47c7bf38b8fd13c0cada115b/50c97/iphone-home-screen-1.jpg 550w,\n/static/a1514d8f47c7bf38b8fd13c0cada115b/b1bff/iphone-home-screen-1.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; background-color: var(--input-background-color); max-width: 800px;\">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 177.8181818181818%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"iPhone apps I use screen shot\" title=\"iPhone apps I use screen shot\" src=\"/static/cf9af7d0911da78055a31cbadadfc721/b1bff/iphone-home-screen-2.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/cf9af7d0911da78055a31cbadadfc721/16841/iphone-home-screen-2.jpg 275w,\n/static/cf9af7d0911da78055a31cbadadfc721/50c97/iphone-home-screen-2.jpg 550w,\n/static/cf9af7d0911da78055a31cbadadfc721/b1bff/iphone-home-screen-2.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; background-color: var(--input-background-color); max-width: 800px;\">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 177.8181818181818%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"more iPhone ass I use screen shot\" title=\"more iPhone ass I use screen shot\" src=\"/static/d79ec325d62517d0339ad4fd31c6dbb2/b1bff/iphone-home-screen-3.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/d79ec325d62517d0339ad4fd31c6dbb2/16841/iphone-home-screen-3.jpg 275w,\n/static/d79ec325d62517d0339ad4fd31c6dbb2/50c97/iphone-home-screen-3.jpg 550w,\n/static/d79ec325d62517d0339ad4fd31c6dbb2/b1bff/iphone-home-screen-3.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n  <figcaption><p>Wouldn&#x2019;t want to leave out the mobile apps I use, so here&#x2019;s my iPhone&#x2019;s home screen.</p></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<h2 id=\"site-stuff\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#site-stuff\" aria-label=\"site stuff permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Site stuff</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Continuous integration and deployment via <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/\"><strong>Travis CI</strong></a>.</li>\n<li>Hosting and CDN via <a href=\"https://www.netlify.com/\"><strong>Netlify</strong></a>.</li>\n<li>Domain name registered with <a href=\"https://hover.com/E4nZJYVH\"><strong>Hover</strong></a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><small>Page may contain affiliate and/or referral links. For more information read my <a href=\"/terms/#disclosure-policy\">disclosure policy</a>.</small></p>","excerpt":"Read on friend to learn about the hardware and software I use for play and to build Made Mistakes. None of it is terribly exciting or…"}},"pageContext":{}}}